<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Savings</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="bg-indigo-950 text-white p-4">
        <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="/home" class="text-2xl font-bold">Budget Buddy</a>
            <div>
                <a href="/home" class="mx-2 hover:underline hover:font-semibold">Home</a>
                <a href="/add" class="mx-2 hover:underline hover:font-semibold">Add Expense</a>
                <a href="/analysis" class="mx-2 hover:underline hover:font-semibold">Analysis</a>
                <a href="/savings" class="mx-2 hover:underline hover:font-semibold">Savings</a>
                <a href="/logout" class="mx-2 hover:underline hover:font-semibold">Log Out</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="bg-gray-200 min-h-screen flex justify-center items-center">
        <img src="/images/analysis.png" alt="image" class="w-92 h-80 mr-40">
        <div class="bg-blue-100 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center max-w-md">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-800 mb-4">Save More!</h2>
            <p class="text-lg mb-2">Your total non-essential spending for this month is <span
                    class="text-red-500 font-bold">₹<%= totalNonEssential.toLocaleString() %></span>.</p>
            <p class="text-lg mb-2">If you were to save 10% of your non-essential expenses, that would be <span
                    class="text-red-500 font-bold">₹<%= tenPercentSavings %></span> per month.</p>
            <p class="text-lg mb-2">If you were to invest those savings at an average 5% return over 10 years,
                compounded monthly, you would save <span class="text-red-500 font-bold">₹<%= futureValue %></span>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>